-Ō£ģ When Queue Depth > 1: How It Works
-When multiple messages are in the queue:
- Multiple Requests in Queue
- The queue depth increases as multiple request messages arrive.
- Each request still has a unique JMSCorrelationID.
- Multiple Consumers Can Process Requests
- If multiple consumers (servers) are listening to the queue, messages are distributed in round-robin fashion.
- Responses Must Have Correct Correlation ID
