-JBoss 8.x (WildFly 8.x) introduces changes that may affect deployments running on JBoss 7.x. Here are the key areas to consider:
-a. Configuration Changes
- Standalone vs. Domain Mode: Ensure the configuration files (standalone.xml, domain.xml, host.xml) are updated based on new schema versions.
- Subsystem Changes:
- Some subsystems may have been removed or replaced (e.g., changes in security, transaction, and messaging configurations).
