-Test Teardown    Close Browser
-
-2. Variables Section
-The Variables section allows you to define and manage data that is used throughout the script. Variables make scripts more flexible, reusable, and easier to maintain.
-Types of Variables in RPA:
- Scalar Variables: Represent single values.
-plaintext
-Copy code
